        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Pricing\n*NEW* Gold Circle Series shows have a two-tiered price structure\nTier 1 (Rows A-E): $95.00 (HST included)\nTier 2 (Rows F-N): $75.00 (HST included)\nClick Here to Buy Tickets!  \nAurora Cultural Centre Presents\nGold Circle Series\n\nZombie Blizzard:\nAaron Davis & Measha"
