        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Aurora Cultural Centre Presents Aurora Winter Blues Festival Crystal Shawanda [...]"
      },
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Click Here to Buy Tickets! \nRegular: $50.00 (HST included)\nStudent: $15.00 (HST included)\nMix & Match Subscription Package (excluding Gold Circle and Family Shows):\nChoose 3+/5+/10+ ACC shows at once and save 15%/20%/25%, respectively!\nDiscount provided at checkout. \nAurora Cultural Centre Presents\nAurora Winter Blues Festival"
      }
    ],
