        "@value": " \n\n\nClick Here to Buy Tickets! \nRegular: $50.00 (HST included)\nStudent: $15.00 (HST included)\nMix & Match Subscription Package (excluding Gold Circle and Family Shows):\nChoose 3+/5+/10+ ACC shows at once and save 15%/20%/25%, respectively!\nDiscount provided at checkout. \nAurora Cultural Centre Presents\n\nMaggie's Wake"
